name: Gymdoll Racerback Active Tank - Cursive - Red/White
description:
You have never worn a tank as awesome as the Gymdoll Active Tank. It is flexible, form-fitting, and so comfortable you will never want to take it off. These tanks are great to wear for killing a workout, or knocking out daily errands. If we had to pick one word to describe these tank tops, it would be “Fanfreakintastic”. (It’s a real word, we wouldn’t make that up!)

  • Cursive Gymdoll Logo with floral up side
  • 4 oz. 98% combed and ring-spun cotton 2% spandex.
  • Super soft feel with a sheer knit fabric that is exceptionally breathable.
  • Designed for a flattering slim fit and extra long body length.
  • This red Active Tank is great for layering.
  • Ideal for: running, weight lifting, yoga, anything!
